return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2023-11-06 06:09:29+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Themes - Twenty Eleven','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['The 2011 theme for WordPress is sophisticated, lightweight, and adaptable. Make it yours with a custom menu, header image, and background -- then go further with available theme options for light or dark color scheme, custom link colors, and three layout choices. Twenty Eleven comes equipped with a Showcase page template that transforms your front page into a showcase to show off your best content, widget support galore (sidebar, three footer areas, and a Showcase page widget area), and a custom "Ephemera" widget to display your Aside, Link, Quote, or Status posts. Included are styles for print and for the admin editor, support for featured images (as custom header images on posts and pages and as large images on featured "sticky" posts), and special styles for six different post formats.'=>'2011 年推出的 Twenty Eleven 是具備最新架構、輕量化及回應式設計的 WordPress 佈景主題；它能讓網站使用自訂選單、頁首圖片、淺色/深色背景，自訂連結色彩及三種版面配置。Twenty Eleven 內建 [文章展示] 頁面範本，這個頁面範本能將網站首頁變成展示精選內容的地方，還包含 6 個小工具區域 (主要資訊欄、3 個頁尾區域及文章展示資訊欄)，以及可顯示文章格式為記事、連結、引文及近況簡述的 [小品內容] 自訂小工具。Twenty Eleven 還包含適用於列印及內容編輯器的樣式，支援精選圖片 (例如文章及頁面的自訂頁首圖片及精選內容/置頂文章上方的大型圖片) 及 6 種文章格式的內容顯示樣式。','Twenty Eleven'=>'Twenty Eleven','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/" target="_blank">Documentation on Theme Customization</a>'=>'〈<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/" target="_blank">佈景主題選項</a>〉線上說明','Blandit. Id ornare arcu odio ut'=>'從零開始學會網路基本觀念','At quis risus sed vulputate odio ut enim'=>'逃避基本觀念可恥卻真的沒有用','Etiam tempor orci eu lobortis'=>'無法逃避的網路基本觀念','Lectus quam id leo in vitae turpis'=>'如何選擇 WordPress 的外掛及佈景主題','Nisi quis eleifend'=>'WordPress 自架站基本觀念','Aenean euismod elementum'=>'如何擺脫 WordPress 的終身新手困境','Talks'=>'演講','Aenean euismod elementum II, 2020'=>'2020 新解「WordPress 不當新手之道」','Blandit. Id ornare arcu odio ut, 2018'=>'2018 新解「勿以惡小而為之，勿以善小而不為」','At quis risus sed vulputate odio ut enim, 2015'=>'2015 新解「蜀道難，難於上青天」','Etiam tempor orci eu lobortis, 2009'=>'2009 新解「道可道，非常道」','Lectus quam id leo in vitae turpis, 2006'=>'2006 新解「大道之行也，天下為公」','Nisi quis eleifend, 1999'=>'1999 新解「唐詩三百首」','Aenean euismod elementum, 1999'=>'1999 新解「古文觀止」','Books'=>'書籍','Two Columns of Lists'=>'2 欄清單','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Nulla porttitor massa id neque aliquam vestibulum morbi blandit cursus. Feugiat nisl pretium fusce id velit. Cursus risus at ultrices mi. Pellentesque nec nam aliquam sem et tortor consequat. Est lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing. Nisi porta lorem mollis aliquam. Aenean euismod elementum nisi quis eleifend quam adipiscing vitae proin. Malesuada bibendum arcu vitae elementum curabitur vitae nunc sed. Quis hendrerit dolor magna eget est lorem ipsum dolor sit. Viverra vitae congue eu consequat.'=>'已家動不們什個南有外因接，聽股感得世神自作教我面著新動省軍實住日春唱清書，樣香國什的眼開們場算數一不坐爸你取裡、高點我，圖是所多天的紀次起驗言把以了古取選子灣任治，同雨部這海：同收國決多輕多隊時一準人把民親才中；那來女的於一次系了。正心反管演數獎應戲夜。代最麼下子生面的，小化管太要研？大研知參賽子裡連。邊熱將早兒不有史；民多者大靈於房兒近紅起阿日大影也不地兒車上師是與天先灣運生企、城步又山良以入車在晚的。作關原學是的進己知，年天國老。路直時吃分交本臺他天我打的陽出減己業近。什眼個統特們竟的雲答通，服金友市界支期總義才帶於住人一使單化一道，一他心明花生人小結新各好生愛滿企系的了斯，隊時一準人把民親。','This is a paragraph to tell about yourself.'=>'可撰寫自我介紹的段落。','About Me'=>'個人簡短說明','Follow'=>'追蹤','Join 1,729 other followers'=>'請加入 1,729 位追蹤者的行列','Click to subscribe to this blog and receive notifications of new posts by email.'=>'點擊以訂閱我的部落格，並接收最新文章的通知電子郵件。','Get In Touch'=>'保持聯絡','Follow Blog'=>'追蹤部落格','Henri Matisse'=>'韓愈','"There are always flowers for those who want to see them."'=>'"千里馬常有，而伯樂不常有。"','Inline Quote'=>'內嵌引文','Aenean euismod elementum nisi quis eleifend. Lectus quam id leo in vitae turpis. Etiam tempor orci eu lobortis elementum nibh. At quis risus sed vulputate odio ut enim blandit. Id ornare arcu odio ut. Blandit massa enim nec dui nunc mattis enim ut tellus. Fermentum iaculis eu non diam phasellus vestibulum. Magna fermentum iaculis eu non diam phasellus vestibulum lorem. Ullamcorper velit sed ullamcorper morbi tincidunt ornare massa. Cursus sit amet dictum sit amet justo donec. At tellus at urna condimentum mattis. Et ligula ullamcorper malesuada proin libero nunc. Ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit duis tristique sollicitudin. Pellentesque diam volutpat commodo sed egestas. Mi proin sed libero enim sed faucibus.'=>'動獨不消教把？有白片，當力她壓通沒里考問是下其行懷企味石證不了教如該，美銷謝表強很委不，收營異持特超上爸去那民。期安存買卻死合客，會天學設音北時地近習失看發小：家斯比元區：到和臺不的機果政人想願人選的顧的防何學線子者是：北活始和漸爭一看有沒我省戰個記！又不綠變她種會了喜決黨計自岸，清決為向成面小布過一建我法的香者想在上動媽此笑灣時風得苦？麼電不花，因親都名是推難道節師過不！親年政他並前的感令。力發乎爾立夠我一非交達子！化東地真的級看！重不出名那請，我下業著把二！爸品不學北有老場子法異容道上心。是著花業能代格、的不其上官又多急近認原事者商變市，車面子爾力主，改維兒，房到人輕造趣現老非水座速度有目對數新陸試農在力定城認不情股速實那。最克他選無畫持時大上的。願家見另？他時她變。活沒發上臺係方手無人行。','This is just an example post to showcase the featured post section on the showcase page. Who doesn&#8217;t like flowers? I like flowers. Nullam hendrerit enim nunc. Vestibulum eget nulla magna! Fusce lobortis neque eu neque egestas tincidunt. Duis elementum consequat lorem, in eleifend justo mollis at. Nam quis adipiscing magna. Duis adipiscing est ac nibh feugiat rhoncus. Donec non lorem felis, eget commodo purus.'=>'這是在展示頁面的精選內容的展示示範文章。口辦現話公金關很地只一教高商，油洲園來園晚散的能味是間地了手不主去成加想後易西無告引們需係前有是同，策身身：路國成灣、醫當不本裡課不要夫品我我師時親成會愛使這，失日也樹包覺有旅？心相康直境去己年世；位車比車吸眼健學女們維。王賽心就叫望，緊古營一而縣作科；變超果別道對說怎間各不間雜界些中的業小臺以，高意日個書子事驗定的的過全，球冷行，後發裡同了收間候也使族科生了但原。','A Bowl Full of&nbsp;Flowers'=>'綻放的鮮花','Image and Text Columns'=>'圖片及文字欄位','Your comment is awaiting moderation. This is a preview; your comment will be visible after it has been approved.'=>'你的留言正在等候審閱。目前顯示的是留言內容的預覽，留言核准後所有人都會看到這則留言。','One thought on &ldquo;%1$s&rdquo;'=>'在〈%1$s〉中有 1 則留言','White'=>'白色','Light Gray'=>'淺灰色','Medium Gray'=>'中灰色','Dark Gray'=>'深灰色','Black'=>'黑色','Blue'=>'藍色','Sidebar Template'=>'資訊欄範本','Showcase Template'=>'文章展示範本','Tag Archives: %s'=>'標籤彙整: %s','Next <span class="meta